caption.p: Phylogeographic range of poultry-adapted H9N2 lineages. Countries where only BJ94 lineage viruses are found shown in red, where only G1-W viruses found shown in blue, where mixtures of BJ94 and G1-E sub-lineage viruses are found shown in orange, where mixtures of BJ94 and G1-W sub-lineage viruses are found shown in purple, where only poultry-adapted Y439-lineage viruses are found shown in light pink.
